&lt;h3 id="example-workflow-with-ai-automation-tools"&gt;Example Workflow with AI Automation Tools&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To visualize how AI automation tools can streamline business processes, consider the following workflow for a marketing team using these tools:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code class="language-mermaid" data-lang="mermaid"&gt;graph TD;
